cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

This paper deals with image classification tasks and investigates the effectiveness of pretrained models on these tasks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also involves machine learning techniques and models, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the performance of different models, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also mentions natural language processing, which could place it under cs.CL (Computation and Language). Finally, the paper discusses adversarial robustness, which could fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
